HEADWORD: Valvata
<hw>Val*va"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.; cf. L.
<ets>valvatus</ets> having folding doors. See <er>Valve</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of small spiral fresh-water gastropods
having an operculum.</def>⟦br⟧
